Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.74,2:01:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我的知更鸟将飞向绿林♪\N♪ My Robin to the greenwood will go ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.57,2:01:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♪橡树和白蜡树所在的地方♪\N♪ Where the oak and the ash ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.88,2:01:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 荆棘丛生 ♪\N♪ And the briars do grow ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.35,2:01:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我的爱人境况如何？♪\N♪ How fares my love ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:41.69,2:01:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 夜幕降临 ♪\N♪ As the darkness falls ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.53,2:01:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 就在那里 ♪\N♪ There within ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.23,2:01:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 那些错综复杂的墙壁？ ♪\N♪ Those tangled walls? ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.54,2:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,♪我的爱人境况如何？♪\N♪ How fares my love ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.97,2:01:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 夜幕降临 ♪\N♪ As the darkness falls ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.87,2:02:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 就在那里 ♪\N♪ There within ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.65,2:02:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 那些错综复杂的墙壁？ ♪\N♪ Those tangled walls? ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.72,2:02:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 绿林就在附近 ♪\N♪ The greenwood is near ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:14.96,2:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 而绿林很远 ♪\N♪ And the greenwood is far ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.39,2:02:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 以及诸多危险 ♪\N♪ And many a danger ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.19,2:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 那里发生了一件人事 ♪\N♪ Befalls a man there ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.00,2:02:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我祈祷那些树 ♪\N♪ I pray that those trees ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:28.40,2:02:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会把我的孩子还给我 ♪\N♪ Will return my boy ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:31.57,2:02:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 献给甜美可爱的罗宾 ♪\N♪ For sweet bonny Robin ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:35.08,2:02:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 这就是我所有的快乐 ♪\N♪ Is all my joy ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.44,2:02:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我祈祷那些树 ♪\N♪ I pray that those trees ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.62,2:02:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 我会把我的孩子还给我 ♪\N♪ Will return my boy ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:45.09,2:02:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 献给甜美可爱的罗宾 ♪\N♪ For sweet bonny Robin ♪
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.35,2:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ 这就是我所有的快乐♪\N♪ Is all my joy. ♪
